# ðŸ”’ Phishing Response Playbook

## Detection
- User reports suspicious emails.
- Email gateway flags malicious links/attachments.

## Response
1. Block malicious sender at email gateway.
2. Invalidate credentials if users clicked links.
3. Forensic analysis of payload (if attachment).

## Prevention
- Conduct phishing awareness training.
- Deploy anti-phishing tools.
- Enable MFA for accounts.
